10 basis points (10 hundredths of a percent) because of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182889155/image_182889155.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745517-fewer-interest-rate-cuts-likely-in-2025-due-to-continued-inflation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:50:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745514", "title": "SOXQ: Strong Growth But Mixed Signals Raise Concerns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Computer Processor Chip\" data-id=\"1715398740\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The semiconductor industry has been one of the best in the tech sector when it comes to reaping the benefits of the AI \u201crevolution\u201d that we\u2019ve seen over the past year or so. As we near the end of the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1715398740/image_1715398740.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745514-soxq-strong-growth-but-mixed-signals-raise-concerns", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:37:04", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745394", "title": "Fed Meeting December 2024: Another Cut Now, But Maybe Fewer Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Federal Reserve ( FED ) to control interest rates. Wooden blocks FED on coins with USA flag background. American economy and business. Federal Reserve Bank Interest rates rise policy. FED concept.\" data-id=\"1703718027\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pcess609</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>No surprise, the Federal Reserve (Fed) cut rates by 25 basis points at its December meeting. But the big surprise was the \u201cdot plot\u201d change for 2025, which shows that the Fed now expects only 50 basis points in cuts next year rather than the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1703718027/image_1703718027.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745394-fed-meeting-december-2024-another-cut-now-maybe-fewer-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745511", "title": "Chemring Stock Tanks But Upside Remains On Double Digit EBITDA Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Apache helicopter\" data-id=\"471581423\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">VanderWolf-Images/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In September, I covered <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4720430-chemring-unlocking-growth-in-defense-and-space\">Chemring</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CMGMF\" title=\"Chemring Group PLC\">OTCPK:CMGMF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CMGMY\" title=\"Chemring Group PLC\">OTCPK:CMGMY</a>) with a buy rating. Since then, the stock has fallen 16% at the <a href=\"https://www.londonstockexchange.com/stock/CHG/chemring-group-plc/company-page\" rel=\"nofollow\">London Stock Exchange</a> where the listing has more liquidity. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/471581423/image_471581423.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745511-chemring-stock-tanks-upside-remains-on-double-digit-ebitda-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:15:51", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745513", "title": "Alibaba: The End Of New Retail As We Know It?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1446944883/image_1446944883.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female Clothing store retail display in shopping mall with discount sales tag\" data-id=\"1446944883\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width