end-of-new-retail-as-we-know-it", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 12:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745509", "title": "H&E Equipment Services: Earnings Understate Cash Production", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Update</h2> <p>Following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4705713-he-equipment-services-unfairly-punished-equipment-rental-play-with-catalysts\">my initial coverage</a> on H&amp;E Equipment Services (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HEES\" title=\"H&amp;E Equipment Services, Inc.\">HEES</a></span>) in July the stock is -6% and there have been several updates to the investment debate. But my views on this business have little changed.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745509-h-and-e-equipment-services-earnings-understate-cash-production", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 11:54:22", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745507", "title": "Norsk Hydro: Getting More Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sunndals\u00f8ra, Norway - June 19, 2022: Aerial view of the Hydro Norse aluminium production facility with a massive power line leading into the industrial complex\" data-id=\"2173687808\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Photofex-AT/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Dear readers/followers,</p> <p>Since my last article on Norsk Hydro (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NHYDY\" title=\"Norsk Hydro ASA\">OTCQX:NHYDY</a>), the company has seen a negative RoR on part with the positive return we saw from my first 2024 article. I typically cover this company</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173687808/image_2173687808.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745507-norsk-hydro-asa-getting-more-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 11:36:44", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745512", "title": "World Economy To Continue Rebalancing In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160631232/image_160631232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Globe on calculator, america map\" data-id=\"160631232\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160631232/image_160631232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160631232/image_160631232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160631232/image_160631232.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160631232/image_160631232.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_ima